headline: Harley-Davidson Earnings Smash Expectations. Why the Stock Is Down.
summary: Tuesday, Harley-Davidson announced third-quarter earnings per share of $3.10 from sales of $1.3 billion. Wall Street was looking for EPS of $1.53 from sales of $1 billion.
